Online Doctor Appointment System

The main purpose of the Doctor Appointment System is to manage the details of the Doctor, Appointment, Patients, Booking, and Doctor Schedule.

  • Created new online presence strategies utilizing my creativity.
  • Provided accurate daily appointment schedules to the doctor.
  • Utilized crucial design software skills to assist with projects.

Recycling waste Management System

The objective of this project is based on environmental protection.Users can book an appointment and can get information about recycling wastes with company information.
